descriptionHtml:
Update 1.9 Hairy - This is just a hairy version of update 1.9 using Navetsea\'s hairy textures. I just transposed them onto the Better Privates skin. Looks good. Check out the screens!

Update 1.9 - Improved textures further. Vagina and nipples look more realistic now. Also repaired the transvaginal texture seam to be less apparent. This is the non-hairy version. Take a look at my screenshots! 

This is my modification to Navetsea\'s CBBE V2V3 1_8 Shaved File. I added some new textures and color adjustments to the vagina and anus. I made some color adjustments to the nipples to make them a bit darker and more \"lush\" (red/pink). I didn\'t over-do it here. Just added a bit of flare and realism to the pretty bits. 

This is just a texture file. Drag and drop into your Skyrim/Data directory.

Of course, you must first download and install the CBBE body for this to work. This is only the texture and maps. 

Remember, these are only tweaks made on Navatsea\'s textures. She/He gets full credit for the origination of this file. I only added some textures and colors to the private bits. It is a bit more XXX this way.

I highly recommend CHSBHC and Victoria\'s High Heel Walk with BBP to compliment this nicely. Killer Keos and Teals Stacked mods have some nice armor/clothing options to go with this body.
